    <item>
      <title>抗议活动过后，孟加拉国放宽宵禁以维持经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bangladesh-factories-banks-stock-market-reopen-as-curfew-eased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国在上周发生致命抗议活动后放宽了全国宵禁，允许主要的服装出口部门和银行重新开业，政府试图让经济重回正轨，并阻止外汇储备的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bangladesh-factories-banks-stock-market-reopen-as-curfew-eased</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:45:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜并不“关心”特朗普对金正恩说的话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/north-korea-does-not-care-about-trump-s-words-for-kim-jong-un</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜国家媒体驳斥了前总统唐纳德·特朗普关于与朝鲜领导人金正恩关系良好的评论，称“我们不在乎”，并警告称，朝鲜的核武库随时准备迎接任何美国领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/north-korea-does-not-care-about-trump-s-words-for-kim-jong-un</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
